{
  "text": "Consistent with this result, no detectable expression of \u03b1-synuclein protein was observed in BL6JHUK in contrast to the 129/Ola and ICR strains (Fig. 1C ). In agreement with previous studies protein levels increased during postnatal development [CITATION_1] , but were consistently absent from the BL6JHUK strain. At prenatal stages (using homogenates from embryo at E14 and brain at E17), \u03b1-synuclein expression was below detection levels in ICR and BL6JHUK animals (data not shown).",
